<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.2.15">
<l>nōkki yacōtai nuṇukkiya mañcaḷāl</l>
<l>nākku vaḻittunī rāṭṭumin nampikku</l>
<l>vākkum nayaṉamu vāyum muṟuvalum</l>
<l>mūkku mirantavā kāṇīrē moykuḻa līrvantu kāṇīrē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Ladies with thick curls, see the quality of the form,</l>
<l>eyes, mouth, teeth, and nose of this lord who,</l>
<l>being seen by Yaśodā, [his] tongue is rubbed</l>
<l>with powdered turmeric and bathed. Come and see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
